TTCut-ng Authors
================

TTCut-ng is developed and maintained by MINIXJR.
  https://github.com/MINIXJR/TTCut-ng

It builds on the following earlier work, whose copyright notices are
kept intact in the source files derived from it:

  TTCut - the original MPEG-2 elementary stream video cutter
    Copyright (c) 2003-2010 B. Altendorf / TriTime
    https://www.tritime.org

  SRT subtitle support (contributed as a pull request to TTCut)
    Copyright (c) 2019 Minei3oat
    https://github.com/Minei3oat

